1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,120
At the age of 25, I'd
made my first million.

2
00:00:03,120 --> 00:00:06,330
It wasn't school that gave me
my education about investing.

3
00:00:06,330 --> 00:00:08,730
My teacher was the rollercoaster of life.

4
00:00:08,730 --> 00:00:10,890
It came to me one day when my boss asked

5
00:00:10,890 --> 00:00:13,650
