help install a staircase.

6
00:00:13,650 --> 00:00:16,530
When we got to the house, I
was shocked, he had it all.

7
00:00:16,530 --> 00:00:18,600
Granite countertops, Persian rugs

8
00:00:18,600 --> 00:00:20,610
and a collection of super cars.

9
00:00:20,610 --> 00:00:21,600
I'd look out the window

10
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:24,480
and see the owner relaxing
or practicing his golf swing.

11
00:00:24,480 --> 00:00:26,190
When I talked to him, he only chatted

12
00:00:26,190 --> 00:00:29,010
about his personal hobbies
and never his businesses.

13
00:00:29,010 --> 00:00:32,070
I asked him, what's the
secret to your success?

14
00:00:32,070 --> 00:00:34,170
He tapped me on the
shoulder and said, Mark,

15
00:00:34,170 --> 00:00:36,330
if you can't make money while you sleep,

16
00:00:36,330 --> 00:00:37,890
you'll work until you die.

17
00:00:37,890 --> 00:00:40,410
This is now known in the
modern day as passive income.

18
00:00:40,410 --> 00:00:43,440
That was the moment I
decided I needed to join

19
00:00:43,440 --> 00:00:45,240
the top 1% of men.

20
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:47,580
I'd like to retread my
journey with you today.

21
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:50,460
It's very clearly broken
into five different stages,

22
00:00:50,460 --> 00:00:53,430
