at each individual stage,

23
00:00:53,430 --> 00:00:56,340
I learned something imperative
to my future success.

24
00:00:56,340 --> 00:00:59,790
You'll learn what I focused on
as a hard-nosed businessman.

25
00:00:59,790 --> 00:01:02,520
What I obsessed about in
the world of investing

26
00:01:02,520 --> 00:01:03,960
and most importantly,

27
00:01:03,960 --> 00:01:05,883
