107
00:04:02,970 --> 00:04:03,870
I went to my boss

108
00:04:03,870 --> 00:04:06,300
and asked him how long I'd
have to keep doing this.

109
00:04:06,300 --> 00:04:08,010
Until the order stopped coming in

110
00:04:08,010 --> 00:04:11,760
which is probably never, he
said, and I felt so deflated.

111
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:14,460
Although I was saving money,
I didn't feel passionate

112
00:04:14,460 --> 00:04:17,640
