176
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:41,370
I started to know more

177
00:06:41,370 --> 00:06:43,230
and more people in the business world.

178
00:06:43,230 --> 00:06:45,810
A lot of these individuals
became my mentors

179
00:06:45,810 --> 00:06:46,860
and would teach me things

180
00:06:46,860 --> 00:06:49,230
like how to build a business that scales,

181
00:06:49,230 --> 00:06:52,320
how to improve sales and
how to manage people.

182
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:54,420
As my income grew and I solved problems,

183
00:06:54,420 --> 00:06:56,310
I was not only growing my net worth

184
00:06:56,310 --> 00:06:58,950
but becoming a top 1% man as well.

185
00:06:58,950 --> 00:07:00,480
As the good times continued,

186
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:02,730
I increasingly bet on them continuing,

187
00:07:02,730 --> 00:07:05,760
which led to one of my most
significant life crashes

188
00:07:05,760 --> 00:07:07,500
and moments of despair.

189
00:07:07,500 --> 00:07:09,420
I remember it like it was yesterday,

190
00:07:09,420 --> 00:07:10,500
walking into the shop

191
00:07:10,500 --> 00:07:13,290
that I had initially started
to give my father a job

192
00:07:13,290 --> 00:07:14,550
in his later years

193
00:07:14,550 --> 00:07:17,670
and instead of being greeted
by the magical emporium filled

194
00:07:17,670 --> 00:07:20,610
