have only dreamed of having

195
00:07:20,610 --> 00:07:24,510
as a kid, I was met with a
smashed roof, empty shelves

196
00:07:24,510 --> 00:07:27,810
and my products laying broken,
thrown across the floor.

197
00:07:27,810 --> 00:07:29,160
This hit me so hard

198
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:32,010
that the memory has been
seared into my subconscious

199
00:07:32,010 --> 00:07:34,710
and I sometimes still see
it when I close my eyes.

200
00:07:34,710 --> 00:07:37,410
You may think, it's all
right Mark, I know you.

201
00:07:37,410 --> 00:07:38,700
I bet you had insurance.

202
00:07:38,700 --> 00:07:41,130
Everything was okay, and you bounced back.

203
00:07:41,130 --> 00:07:43,770
Well, in fact, I'd grown so fast

204
00:07:43,770 --> 00:07:45,510
and I was making so much money

205
00:07:45,510 --> 00:07:47,610
that not everything was
correctly structured

206
00:07:47,610 --> 00:07:48,600
within my business.

207
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:51,330
Although we were insured,
I'd forgotten to update it

208
00:07:51,330 --> 00:07:53,970
