disaster doesn't stop there.

210
00:07:56,790 --> 00:07:58,320
It gets even worse.

211
00:07:58,320 --> 00:08:00,157
I got a phone call a few days later

212
00:08:00,157 --> 00:08:01,890
and one of my staff informed me

213
00:08:01,890 --> 00:08:04,350
