220
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:17,910
and the damage was horrendous,

221
00:08:17,910 --> 00:08:19,800
let alone the stock that we lost.

222
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:20,633
That's when I learned

223
00:08:20,633 --> 00:08:23,370
